cscf_Registered_Users: select sum(cscfConcurrentRegisteredUserProfiles)+sum(scscfConcurrentUnregisteredUserProfiles) as Measure_Value from DC_E_IMS_CSCF2_RAW where utc_datetime_id=@time and G3MANAGEDELEMENT=@node and ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') and (MOID like '%400%' or MOID like '%401%' or MOID like '%403%' or MOID like '%DEFAULT%' or MOID like '%SUM%' or MOID like '%sum%') group by dc_release,oss_id,G3MANAGEDELEMENT,utc_datetime_id
mtas_Initial_Registrations: select ((SUM(MtasSubsDataInitialRegOk)+sum(MtasSubsDataAutoRegOk))/(60*period_duration)) AS Measure_Value from DC_E_MTAS_MTASSUBSDATA_RAW where utc_datetime_id=@time and G3MANAGEDELEMENT=@node group by dc_release,oss_id,G3MANAGEDELEMENT,utc_datetime_id,period_duration
mtas_Registration_Completion: select (100*((sum(MtasSubsDataDeregOk)+sum(MtasSubsDataReregOk))/(sum(MtasSubsDataDeregOk)   +sum(MtasSubsDataDeregNOkE)+sum(MtasSubsDataDeregNOkI)+sum(MtasSubsDataReregOk)+sum(MtasSubsDataReregNOkE)+sum(MtasSubsDataReregNOkI)))) as Measure_Value  from DC_E_MTAS_MTASSUBSDATA_RAW   where utc_datetime_id=@time   and G3MANAGEDELEMENT=@node group by dc_release,oss_id,G3MANAGEDELEMENT,utc_datetime_id
mtas_Active_Users: select avg(MtasFuncOngoingSess) as Measure_Value  from DC_E_MTAS_MTASTRAF_RAW where utc_datetime_id=@time   and G3MANAGEDELEMENT=@node group by dc_release,oss_id,G3MANAGEDELEMENT,utc_datetime_id
sbg_Reregistration_Success: select 100*((sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATREREGACCCNT)+sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATREJREREGCNT400)+sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATREJREREGCNT403))/(sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATREREGATTCNT))) as Measure_Value from((SELECT DISTINCT D1.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE,D1.NE_ID AS NEID,D1.OSS_ID AS OSSID,sum(D1.sbgSipRegStatReRegAccCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREREGACCCNT,sum(D1.sbgSipRegStatRejReRegCnt400) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJREREGCNT400,sum(D1.sbgSipRegStatRejReRegCnt403) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJREREGCNT403,sum(D1.sbgSipRegStatReRegAttCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREREGATTCNT, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID FROM  DC_E_IMSSBG_PROXYREGISTRAR_RAW D1 WHERE D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED')group by D1.DC_RELEASE,D1.NE_ID,D1.OSS_ID,D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID,D1.sbgSipRegStatReRegAccCnt,D1.sbgSipRegStatRejReRegCnt400,D1.sbgSipRegStatRejReRegCnt403,D1.sbgSipRegStatReRegAttCnt)UNION(SELECT DISTINCT D2.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE,D2.NE_ID AS NEID,D2.OSS_ID AS OSSID,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatReRegAccCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREREGACCCNT,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatRejReRegCnt400) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJREREGCNT400,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatRejReRegCnt403) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJREREGCNT403,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatReRegAttCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREREGATTCNT,D2.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID FROM  DC_E_IMSSBG_PROXYREGISTRARV6_RAW D2 WHERE D2.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED')group by D2.DC_RELEASE,D2.NE_ID,D2.OSS_ID,D2.UTC_DATETIME_ID,D2.sbgSipRegStatReRegAccCnt,D2.sbgSipRegStatRejReRegCnt400,D2.sbgSipRegStatRejReRegCnt403,D2.sbgSipRegStatReRegAttCnt)) a where NEID=@node and UTCDATETIMEID=@time group by a.DCRELEASE,a.NEID,a.OSSID,a.UTCDATETIMEID
sbg_Initial_Registration_Success: select 100*((sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATINITIALACCCNT)+sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATREJINITIALREGCN400)+sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATREJINITIALREGCN403)+sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATREJINITIALREGCN404))/(sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATINITIALATTCNT))) as Measure_Value from((SELECT DISTINCT D1.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE,D1.NE_ID AS NEID,D1.OSS_ID AS OSSID,D1.sbgSipRegStatInitialAccCnt AS SBGSIPREGSTATINITIALACCCNT,D1.sbgSipRegStatInitialAttCnt AS SBGSIPREGSTATINITIALATTCNT,D1.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt400 AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJINITIALREGCN400,D1.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt403 AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJINITIALREGCN403,D1.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt404 AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJINITIALREGCN404,D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID FROM DC_E_IMSSBG_PROXYREGISTRAR_RAW D1 WHERE D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED')group by D1.DC_RELEASE,D1.NE_ID,D1.OSS_ID,D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID,D1.sbgSipRegStatInitialAccCnt,D1.sbgSipRegStatInitialAttCnt,D1.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt400 ,D1.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt403,D1.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt404)UNION(SELECT DISTINCT D2.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE,D2.NE_ID AS NEID,D2.OSS_ID AS OSSID,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatInitialAccCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATINITIALACCCNT,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatInitialAttCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATINITIALATTCNT,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt400) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJINITIALREGCN400,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt403) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJINITIALREGCN403,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt404) AS SBGSIPREGSTATREJINITIALREGCN404,D2.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID FROM DC_E_IMSSBG_PROXYREGISTRARV6_RAW D2 WHERE D2.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED')group by D2.DC_RELEASE,D2.NE_ID,D2.OSS_ID,D2.UTC_DATETIME_ID,D2.sbgSipRegStatInitialAccCnt,D2.sbgSipRegStatInitialAttCnt,D2.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt400,D2.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt403,D2.sbgSipRegStatRejInitialRegCnt404)) a where NEID=@node and UTCDATETIMEID=@time group by a.DCRELEASE,a.NEID,a.OSSID,a.UTCDATETIMEID
sbg_Deregistration_Success: select 100*((sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATDEREGACCCNT))/(sum(a.SBGSIPREGSTATDEREGATTCNT))) as Measure_Value from((SELECT  DISTINCT D1.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE,D1.NE_ID AS NEID,D1.OSS_ID AS OSSID,sum(D1.sbgSipRegStatDeRegAccCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATDEREGACCCNT,sum(D1.sbgSipRegStatDeRegAttCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATDEREGATTCNT,D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID FROM DC_E_IMSSBG_PROXYREGISTRAR_RAW D1 WHERE D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED')group by D1.DC_RELEASE,D1.NE_ID,D1.OSS_ID,D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID,D1.sbgSipRegStatDeRegAccCnt,D1.sbgSipRegStatDeRegAttCnt)UNION(SELECT  DISTINCT D2.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE,D2.NE_ID AS NEID,D2.OSS_ID AS OSSID,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatDeRegAccCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATDEREGACCCNT,sum(D2.sbgSipRegStatDeRegAttCnt) AS SBGSIPREGSTATDEREGATTCNT,D2.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID FROM DC_E_IMSSBG_PROXYREGISTRARV6_RAW D2 WHERE D2.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED')group by D2.DC_RELEASE,D2.NE_ID,D2.OSS_ID,D2.UTC_DATETIME_ID,D2.sbgSipRegStatDeRegAccCnt,D2.sbgSipRegStatDeRegAttCnt)) a where NEID=@node and UTCDATETIMEID=@time group by a.DCRELEASE,a.NEID,a.OSSID,a.UTCDATETIMEID
sbg_Total_Registered_Users: select avg(sbgSgcRegResCurrentTotalReg) as Measure_Value from DC_E_IMSSBG_SGC_RAW where utc_datetime_id=@time and NE_ID=@node group by dc_release,oss_id,NE_ID,utc_datetime_id
mrs_Traffic_Load: SELECT avg(D1.pmNrOfMediaStreamChannelsBusy)/2.005 AS PMNROFMEDIASTREAMCHANNELSBUS FROM DC_E_MGW_MGWAPPLICATION_RAW D1 WHERE D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID=@time and NEUN=@node and D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') and D1.MGW IN (select DISTINCT NE_NAME from DIM_e_CN_Mgw WHERE NE_TYPE like '%Mrf%' or NE_TYPE like '%Bgf%' OR NE_TYPE like 'Im-Mgw') group by D1.DC_RELEASE, D1.MGW, D1.OSS_ID, D1.PERIOD_DURATION, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID

sbg_Memory_Usage: SELECT avg(D1.sbgSgcCritResCpMemoryPercent) AS SBGSGCCRITRESCPMEMORYPERCENT FROM DC_E_IMSSBG_SGCCP_RAW D1 WHERE D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID =@time and NE_ID=@node and D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') group by D1.DC_RELEASE, D1.NE_ID, D1.OSS_ID, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID

hssfe_User_Authorization_Query_Requests: select ((sum(CxQuery3gppRequests))/(60*(PERIOD_DURATION))) as kpi from DC_E_HSS_HSS_RAW where utc_datetime_id=@time and g3ManagedElement=@node and ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') group by dc_release,oss_id,g3ManagedElement,utc_datetime_id,period_duration

cscf_Memory_Usage: SELECT D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID, avg(D1.MemUsage) AS MEMUSAGE, D1.g3ManagedElement AS G3MANAGEDELEMENT, D1.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE, D1.OSS_ID AS OSSID FROM DC_E_IMS_PLTFMEAS_RAW D1 WHERE D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID=@time and G3MANAGEDELEMENT=@node and D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') group by D1.DC_RELEASE, D1.g3ManagedElement, D1.OSS_ID, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID
cscf_CPU_Load: SELECT D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID, avg(D1.DicosCpuLoad) AS DICOSCPULOAD, D1.g3ManagedElement AS G3MANAGEDELEMENT, D1.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE, D1.OSS_ID AS OSSID FROM DC_E_IMS_PLTFMEAS_RAW D1 WHERE D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID =@time and G3MANAGEDELEMENT=@node and D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') group by D1.DC_RELEASE, D1.g3ManagedElement, D1.OSS_ID, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID
mtas_Initial_Registrations_Success: select 100*(MTASSUBSDATAINITIALREGOK)/(MTASSUBSDATAINITIALREGOK+MTASSUBSDATAINITIALREGNOKE+MTASSUBSDATAINITIALREGNOKI) from ( SELECT D1.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE, D1.g3ManagedElement AS G3MANAGEDELEMENT, sum(D1.MtasSubsDataInitialRegNOkE) AS MTASSUBSDATAINITIALREGNOKE, sum(D1.MtasSubsDataInitialRegNOkI) AS MTASSUBSDATAINITIALREGNOKI, sum(D1.MtasSubsDataInitialRegOk) AS MTASSUBSDATAINITIALREGOK, D1.OSS_ID AS OSSID, D1.PERIOD_DURATION AS PERIODDURATION, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID FROM DC_E_MTAS_MTASSUBSDATA_RAW D1 WHERE D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') and D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID =@time and G3MANAGEDELEMENT=@node group by D1.OSS_ID, D1.g3ManagedElement, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID, D1.DC_RELEASE, D1.PERIOD_DURATION) a
hssfe_No_of_Users: SELECT D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID, D1.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE, D1.NE_ID AS NEID, D1.OSS_ID AS OSSID, avg(D1.TotalNumberOfActiveImsUsers) AS TOTALNUMBEROFACTIVEIMSUSERS FROM DC_E_CUDB_HSS_ISMACTIVEUSERS_RAW D1 WHERE D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID ='18/5/2022 6:00:00 AM' and NE_ID='HSS-FE' AND D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') group by UTC_DATETIME_ID,DC_RELEASE,NE_ID,OSS_ID
cscf_Call_Attempts: select sum(kpi) as final from (select sum(((CSCFORIGINATINGINVITETOASATT)+CSCFTERMINATINGINVITETOASATT+SCSCFTERMINATINGINVITENOASAT+SCSCFORIGINATINGINVITENOASAT)/((CSCFCONCURRENTREGISTEREDUSER)+(SCSCFCONCURRENTUNREGISTEREDU))) as kpi,UTCDATETIMEID from ( SELECT D1.cscfConcurrentRegisteredUserProfiles AS CSCFCONCURRENTREGISTEREDUSER, D1.cscfOriginatingInviteToAsAttempts AS CSCFORIGINATINGINVITETOASATT, D1.cscfTerminatingInviteToAsAttempts AS CSCFTERMINATINGINVITETOASATT, D1.DC_RELEASE AS DCRELEASE, D1.g3ManagedElement AS G3MANAGEDELEMENT, D1.MOID AS MOID, D1.OSS_ID AS OSSID, D1.scscfConcurrentUnregisteredUserProfiles AS SCSCFCONCURRENTUNREGISTEREDU, D1.scscfTerminatingInviteNoAsAttempts AS SCSCFTERMINATINGINVITENOASAT, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID, D1.scscfOriginatingInviteNoAsAttempts AS SCSCFORIGINATINGINVITENOASAT FROM DC_E_IMS_CSCF2_RAW D1 WHERE D1.date_id = @time and D1.G3MANAGEDELEMENT=@node and hour_id=@hour and D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED')and (D1.MOID like '%400%' or D1.MOID like '%401%' or D1.MOID like '%403%' or D1.MOID like '%DEFAULT%' or D1.MOID like '%SUM%' or D1.MOID like '%sum%'))a group by UTCDATETIMEID)b
